net.sf.beezle.mork.classfile

Class Input

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.beezle.mork.classfile.Input
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constants

    public class Input
extends Object
implements Constants
    A context to read a class file. The context is comprised of an input stream and a constant pool.
